{"tid":1202054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家坐同一條船唔好再互相質疑啦","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T08:03:26.000Z","uid":220074,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc88da548d47df9b206c28b859f3c9f2cf2d85ee","tid":1202054,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"無論係個晚凌晨得返幾百個後生仔定係其他都好，<br />\n（個晚真係好多人包括我自己都唔係有心想走，<br />\n一個女仔俾幾個警察圍住幾咁無助希望你哋明）<br />\n<br />\n大家都係坐係同一條船都係反送中<br />\n唔好再因為啲小事去搞到大家唔開心啦<br />\n希望大家今晚同聽朝都團結<br />\n見到有事 唔該幫手 唔好縮沙 唔好得個講字。<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好再見到有人又留話我得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋可以唔聽，但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港會玩完</span></span> 自己選擇<br />\n你哋選擇聽一次團結一次，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港仲有機會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見，香港精神 博盡無悔 </span></span>"},{"pid":"43e8559fde28f29e08b2d2a8c816284d36d1acbd","tid":1202054,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"見到有自己人咬自己人真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明大家嘅出發點同目的都一樣都係想香港好<br />\n點解唔互相幫助互相撐大家<br />\n而要去質疑？大家都付出咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844d2f5113f7c933c7b756cf7041a1a079319396","tid":1202054,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"大家有咩物資需要<br />\n或者有好心人肯幫我搬下物資嘅留TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：6.9自己搬咗一箱去好快無曬先想提供多啲，但係一個人搬唔到咁多，求下今晚得閒嘅巴絲幫手。"},{"pid":"37b9b66c192113181eec0d9b33b311237c6c2806","tid":1202054,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"真係平時唔求人，<br />\n呢次為香港真係係咁求人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549dc376d2e0c304e7d8eb4e594cb09d134414d2","tid":1202054,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"唔做鍵盤戰士啦 繼續準備物資好過<br />\n希望大家幫推 自己推太曬時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}